          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="features__feature">
          <div class="features__icon">
            <svg>
              {{! <use xlink:href="img/icons.svg#icon-trending-up"></use> }}
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h5 class="features__header">Find the peace you've always wanted</h5>
